name: Ext_R5_ConceptMap_identifier
title: Cross-version Extension for R5.ConceptMap.identifier for use in FHIR R4
description: This cross-version extension represents ConceptMap.identifier from http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/ConceptMap|5.0.0 for use in FHIR R4.

element.short: Additional identifier for the concept map
element.definition: A formal identifier that is used to identify this concept map when it is represented in other formats, or referenced in a specification, model, design or an instance.
element.comment: `ConceptMap.identifier` maps to R4 `ConceptMap.identifier`. So is mapped as Equivalent.
